<br>
Author: scifichick774<br>
<br>
Rating: R<br>
<br>
Category: Drama/Angst<br>
<br>
Spoilers: Bits and pieces from seasons 1 and 2<br>
<br>
Summary: A serial killer strikes Clark County in the middle of summer.<br>
